te change is stalking the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 359, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Climate change\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 328}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier this week in Paris, dozens of social activists from the organization Extinction Rebellionattemptedto peacefully protest the ways the Olympics are harming Paris and the wider environment.\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 381, \"end\": 386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2077081008449595e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 522, \"end\": 527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2077081008449595e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"dozens\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 394}, {\"ngram\": \"social activists\", \"from\": 398, \"to\": 414}, {\"ngram\": \"the organization\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 436}, {\"ngram\": \"Extinction Rebellionattemptedto\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 468}, {\"ngram\": \"the ways\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 496}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 509}, {\"ngram\": \"the wider environment\", \"from\": 532, \"to\": 553}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But before they were able to carry out their action on the Pont des Arts bridge over the Seine, police swooped in and preemptively arrested them.\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 700, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 614, \"end\": 627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_des_Arts\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pont des Arts\", \"types\": [\"Q12280\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_des_Arts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_des_Arts\"}, {\"begin\": 644, \"end\": 649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0390266255609102e-14, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their action\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 606}, {\"ngram\": \"police\", \"from\": 651, \"to\": 657}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A group of journalists were trapped alongside them as they wereencircledby the heavily armed authorities wearing Paris 2024 Olympics patches on their shoulders.\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 861, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A group\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 708}, {\"ngram\": \"journalists\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 723}, {\"ngram\": \"the heavily armed authorities\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 805}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 819}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics patches\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 841}, {\"ngram\": \"their shoulders\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 860}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The activists' demonstration could also be read as solidarity with the athletes in events like the triathlon and marathon swim.\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 990, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The activists' demonstration\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 891}, {\"ngram\": \"solidarity\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 924}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 942}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 952}, {\"ngram\": \"the triathlon\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 971}, {\"ngram\": \"marathon swim\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These world-class competitors are slated to compete in the murky waters, if they meet safety standards.\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1094, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These world-class competitors\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"the murky waters\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1062}, {\"ngram\": \"safety standards\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1093}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(They do not as of this writing.)\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1128, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this writing\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1126}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French Olympic security forces smothered an urgent message: The world is on fire, and mega-events like the Olympics are hastening environmental calamity.\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1130, \"end\": 1136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.97747409681423, \"rank\": 0.019646641315390855, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an urgent message\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1188}, {\"ngram\": \"The world\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1199}, {\"ngram\": \"fire\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1210}, {\"ngram\": \"mega\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1220}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1227}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1245}, {\"ngram\": \"environmental calamity\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These kinds of mega-events typically leave a harmful ecological legacy.\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1355, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These kinds\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1295}, {\"ngram\": \"mega\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1303}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1310}, {\"ngram\": \"a harmful ecological legacy\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Paris 2024 organizers said that these games would be different.\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1423, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1360, \"end\": 1370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1450712397887377e-32, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these games\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Theymadesustainability a centerpiece of their rhetoric.\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1479, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Theymadesustainability\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1446}, {\"ngram\": \"a centerpiece\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1460}, {\"ngram\": \"their rhetoric\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1478}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Theypledgedthat the Games will be \\\"historic for the climate,\\\" thegreenestGames in the history of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1505}, {\"ngram\": \"the climate\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1539}, {\"ngram\": \"the history\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1573}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The reality, as Extinction Rebellion was trying to convey, has been quite different.\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1675, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The reality\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1602}, {\"ngram\": \"Extinction Rebellion\", \"from\": 1607, \"to\": 1627}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The reality is that the very idea of gigantic sporting extravaganzas like the Olympic Games must be radically reevaluated if the world is to meet theParis Agreement's climate emissions targets by 2050.\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1877, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The reality\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1687}, {\"ngram\": \"the very idea\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1709}, {\"ngram\": \"gigantic sporting extravaganzas\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1744}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1767}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1801, \"to\": 1810}, {\"ngram\": \"theParis Agreement's climate emissions targets\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1868}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the early 1990s, power brokers in the Olympic movement allied, at least rhetorically, to address the climate crisis.\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1998, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the early 1990s\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1897}, {\"ngram\": \"power brokers\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1912}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic movement\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 1936}, {\"ngram\": \"the climate crisis\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 1997}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One academic analysis, however,revealedthat when it came to the sustainability practices of 16 Olympics stretching from 1992 to 2020, environmental follow-through was severely lacking.\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2183, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One academic analysis\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2020}, {\"ngram\": \"the sustainability practices\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2087}, {\"ngram\": \"16 Olympics\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2102}, {\"ngram\": \"environmental follow-through\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2161}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, the four least \\\"sustainable\\\" Olympics-Sochi 2014, Rio 2016, Tokyo 2020, and London 2012-were all relatively recent.\", \"from\": 2184, \"to\": 2308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2243, \"end\": 2246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Earth_Summit\", \"score\": 0.999954764876705, \"rank\": 4.523716627545097e-05, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Earth_Summit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Earth_Summit\"}, {\"begin\": 2253, \"end\": 2258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.178269405608164e-13, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2269, \"end\": 2280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.75