m\": \"a long way\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here in Paris, we met up with Madeleine Orr, assistant professor of sports ecology at the University of Toronto and author ofWarming Up: How Climate Change Is Changing Sports.\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2880, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2713, \"end\": 2718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2077081008449595e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2735, \"end\": 2748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madeleine_Orr\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Madeleine Orr\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madeleine_Orr\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madeleine_Orr\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"assistant professor\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2769}, {\"ngram\": \"sports ecology\", \"from\": 2773, \"to\": 2787}, {\"ngram\": \"the University\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2805}, {\"ngram\": \"Toronto\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2816}, {\"ngram\": \"author\", \"from\": 2821, \"to\": 2827}, {\"ngram\": \"Climate Change\", \"from\": 2846, \"to\": 2860}, {\"ngram\": \"Sports\", \"from\": 2873, \"to\": 2879}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the shadow of the Eiffel Tower, she bluntly stated, \\\"A sustainable Olympics is an oxymoron.\", \"from\": 2881, \"to\": 2975, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the shadow\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2894}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 2898, \"to\": 2914}, {\"ngram\": \"A sustainable Olympics\", \"from\": 2937, \"to\": 2959}, {\"ngram\": \"an oxymoron\", \"from\": 2963, \"to\": 2974}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the [Olympic] model is completely untenable.\", \"from\": 2976, \"to\": 3024, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the [Olympic] model\", \"from\": 2980, \"to\": 2999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are not going be able to continue to do it much longer.\\\"\", \"from\": 3025, \"to\": 3086, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In other words, the IOC and local host organizing committees engage in \\\"greenwashing\\\"-saying they care for the environment while doing very little, if anything, to materially address the ecological problems that plague our world.\", \"from\": 3088, \"to\": 3317, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3108, \"end\": 3111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8740691515975628e-33, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other words\", \"from\": 3091, \"to\": 3102}, {\"ngram\": \"local host organizing committees\", \"from\": 3116, \"to\": 3148}, {\"ngram\": \"the environment\", \"from\": 3195, \"to\": 3210}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 3239, \"to\": 3247}, {\"ngram\": \"the ecological problems\", \"from\": 3271, \"to\": 3294}, {\"ngram\": \"our world\", \"from\": 3307, \"to\": 3316}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This absence of genuine sustainability can be seen in the saga of the aforementioned river.\", \"from\": 3319, \"to\": 3410, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This absence\", \"from\": 3319, \"to\": 3331}, {\"ngram\": \"genuine sustainability\", \"from\": 3335, \"to\": 3357}, {\"ngram\": \"the saga\", \"from\": 3373, \"to\": 3381}, {\"ngram\": \"the aforementioned river\", \"from\": 3385, \"to\": 3409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Franceinvestedsome $1.5 billion to make the Seine swimmable for the first time in more than a century.\", \"from\": 3411, \"to\": 3513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3455, \"end\": 3460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0390266255609102e-14, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Franceinvestedsome\", \"from\": 3411, \"to\": 3429}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 3475, \"to\": 3489}, {\"ngram\": \"more than a century\", \"from\": 3493, \"to\": 3512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was an audacious goal given the amount of sewage, toxic plastic, trash, agricultural run-off, and pharmaceutical refuse dumped in the storied body of water over decades of industrialization.\", \"from\": 3514, \"to\": 3707, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an audacious goal\", \"from\": 3521, \"to\": 3538}, {\"ngram\": \"the amount\", \"from\": 3545, \"to\": 3555}, {\"ngram\": \"sewage\", \"from\": 3559, \"to\": 3565}, {\"ngram\": \"toxic plastic\", \"from\": 3567, \"to\": 3580}, {\"ngram\": \"trash\", \"from\": 3582, \"to\": 3587}, {\"ngram\": \"agricultural run-off\", \"from\": 3589, \"to\": 3609}, {\"ngram\": \"pharmaceutical refuse\", \"from\": 3615, \"to\": 3636}, {\"ngram\": \"the storied body\", \"from\": 3647, \"to\": 3663}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 3667, \"to\": 3672}, {\"ngram\": \"decades\", \"from\": 3678, \"to\": 3685}, {\"ngram\": \"industrialization\", \"from\": 3689, \"to\": 3706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the days before the Olympics there were two swimming spectacles staged by the leadership to showcase their green efforts, with French Sports Minister Am\\u00e9lie Oud\\u00e9a-Cast\\u00e9rataking a dipin the river before Paris's socialist Mayor Anne Hidalgofollowed throughon her promise to do the same.\", \"from\": 3709, \"to\": 3996, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3914, \"end\": 3919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2077081008449595e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\